Chinaman
Homonym Number: 1
Word Class:noun
Sense Number:
Definition:cement-stone; (usu. pl) a large stone found in gold-bearing gravels etc.; large blocks of <i>cement</i>
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Domain:[none]
Region:[none]
